{
  "message": "\ud83c\udf31 Add ClusterGroups component and index exports\n\n- Extract ClusterGroups component with form handling\n- Add index.ts for cleaner imports from components/\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nSigned-off-by: Andrew Anderson <andy@clubanderson.com>",
  "files": [
    {
